{"tid":828651,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[亞洲籃球] 澳門非凡12及FIBA亞冠盃討論區  18/9-2/10","createTime":"2018-09-20T00:10:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T05:34:26.000Z","uid":18692,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"07105829564bee9a277e6935287363ba0a633997","tid":828651,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T00:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/d509e0f0ee600a98705ac0fbaf49bda6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fd509e0f0ee600a98705ac0fbaf49bda6.jpg&h=fef1e203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">非凡12（Asia League主辦）<br />\n<br />\n9月18日至20日（分組賽）  <br />\n9月22日（4強）<br />\n9月23日（決賽及季軍戰）<br />\n<br />\n球場：新濠影匯綜藝館, 澳門</span><br />\n<br />\n非凡12是重磅季前賽。12支亞洲頂級籃球隊將一較高下&mdash;&mdash;4隊來自CBA，3隊日本B.League，南韓KBL和台灣SBL各有2隊及1隊菲律賓明星隊。所有球隊都以包括2名外籍球員在內的最強陣容出戰，爭奪冠軍。"},{"pid":"aa9e7b7af1bea5a6ba049e25432a6e295a68b50d","tid":828651,"uid":18692,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T00:10:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AsiaLeagueOfficial\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAsiaLeagueOfficial&d=9HFwKgiXanrvJ1lsAHvQR%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=1133c4fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AsiaLeagueOfficial</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCE--r0UnH4KFVBtFVHN5jeA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCE--r0UnH4KFVBtFVHN5jeA&d=9HFwKgiXanrvJ1lsAHvQR%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=657449ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCE--r0UnH4KFVBtFVHN5jeA</a><br />\n直播links <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d84d845b8e06fb2d0cd23876304eda1bd855baba","tid":828651,"uid":18692,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T00:14:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">分組名單<br />\nA組：名古屋鑽石海豚 (日本)、裕隆納智捷 (台灣)、浙江猛獅 (中國) <br />\nB組：廣州龍獅 (中國)、千葉噴射機 (日本)、蔚山現代太陽神 (南韓)<br />\nC組：琉球黃金帝王 (日本)、新疆飛虎 (中國)、發展聯盟明星隊 (菲律賓)<br />\nD組：富邦勇士 (台灣)、首爾三星閃電 (南韓)、山東金星 (中國)</span><br />\n<br />\n每組首名晉級4強"},{"pid":"9a01db533191439057fa545628700c64e95db5d4","tid":828651,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T01:01:29.000Z","msg":"分組賽票價為MOP/HKD 100，VIP門票為$250，一日門票可以睇晒4場分組賽。<br />\n<br />\n而4強 (22日)及決賽日(23日)為MOP/HKD 120，VIP門票為$400 。可以睇晒2場準決賽或季軍戰及決賽，仲可以近距離觀賞前NBA球員，包括明星級中鋒Al Jefferson, 前勇士總冠軍成員Marreese Speights和林志傑，羅健兒及富樫勇樹等亞洲一線球員。<br />\n<br />\n新濠影滙位處路氹城，可於港澳碼頭及氹仔碼頭乘搭穿梭巴士前往   <br />\n<br />\n售票網<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theasialeague.com/tickets/?lang=zh-hant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theasialeague.com%2Ftickets%2F%3Flang%3Dzh-hant&d=9HFwKgiXanrvJ1lsAHvQR%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=2384629f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theasialeague.com/tickets/?lang=zh-hant</a>"},{"pid":"3c03774c9a4e516f21ca78b9033a78749d737fe4","tid":828651,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T01:25:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">今日賽程<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">15:00 名古屋鑽石海豚 vs 浙江猛獅</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>17:00 千葉噴射機 vs 蔚山現代太陽神</span></strong><br />\n19:00 新疆飛虎 vs  菲律賓發展聯盟明星隊<br />\n21:00 富邦勇士 vs 山東金星 </span>"},{"pid":"2ca9db0b03f62adbdf65ebc1d3419514b8f275f4","tid":828651,"uid":52,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T01:31:28.000Z","msg":"冇左富樫唔駛睇千葉<br />\n仲諗住澳門近近地可以睇多次佢打波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b69f161bf4330208ca9130792b6e3bc2468450","tid":828651,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:42:18.000Z","msg":"分組賽賽果<br />\nA組<br />\n裕隆納智捷 72-84  名古屋鑽石海豚<br />\n浙江猛獅 96-64 裕隆納智捷<br />\n<br />\nB組<br />\n千葉噴射機 83-92 廣州龍獅<br />\n蔚山現代太陽神 97-98 (OT) 廣州龍獅<br />\n<br />\nC組<br />\n琉球黃金帝王 103- 75 菲律賓