9fe4fac88d1cace9aa1a6fc681_1531122428.webp%3Fv%3D1536144598&h=376d38e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而我自己就買左2樓指定席<br />\n<img src=\"https://chibajets.jp/files/rcms_conv_webp/8/f/8f12d08138c655ec1aa6743f53a9c17f_1531122428.webp?v=1536144597\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchibajets.jp%2Ffiles%2Frcms_conv_webp%2F8%2Ff%2F8f12d08138c655ec1aa6743f53a9c17f_1531122428.webp%3Fv%3D1536144597&h=038965a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://chibajets.jp/files/user/tix/2018-19/2018-19_tix_map_funabashi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchibajets.jp%2Ffiles%2Fuser%2Ftix%2F2018-19%2F2018-19_tix_map_funabashi.png&h=ba4f5a82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拎波飛既方法我就揀左係familymart裡面既機印出黎，因為我唔識日文費事有咩禁錯，去同店員雞同鴨講做下手勢佢就幫我去部機搞，部機禁完一次會出左張單之類既野(好似係)，個時我唔識禁完呢張出黎就行出門口，好彩個店員拉返住我，佢要埋位拎返張單黎PRINT張飛出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/122912_8b2f72395bf43453623a8a7806ab54ec.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F122912_8b2f72395bf43453623a8a7806ab54ec.JPG&h=a53bd614&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n船橋站已經有poster<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/150256_5251ce7c1cbd2df0be07fbeaa819dd16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F150256_5251ce7c1cbd2df0be07fbeaa819dd16.jpg&h=8cb7bc55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ngoogle map都慳返唔駛用，因為跟住動物大遷徙就去到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/150751_d35972baa1280fb7d7181fe5f14253dc.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F150751_d35972baa1280fb7d7181fe5f14253dc.jpeg&h=fbe76519&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n地下有商品賣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/150248_9faecf34ffcbd871129414479f8d4265.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F150248_9faecf34ffcbd871129414479f8d4265.jpeg&h=ad719f3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二樓賣小食<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/150247_7850961f4453ebea64e324ffa740af4b.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F150247_7850961f4453ebea64e324ffa740af4b.jpeg&h=e9515327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結算係地下，但多人到都排上二樓<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/150253_fc2d36535830867050542e903fd9cea9.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F150253_fc2d36535830867050542e903fd9cea9.jpeg&h=ea6df107&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩邊熱身<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/150251_1e4a01f9a1714ff6e20feb915bbb3b8d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F150251_1e4a01f9a1714ff6e20feb915bbb3b8d.jpeg&h=0f0e0eb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/150252_09c418774cf2e7648f187a7e30eeeaed.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F150252_09c418774cf2e7648f187a7e30eeeaed.jpeg&h=92668f4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n田臥<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/150245_808ef63748c8a530fee6c9aaac1f3ad3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F150245_808ef63748c8a530fee6c9aaac1f3ad3.jpeg&h=4612bca5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開場會有煙火煙霧效果，冇影相但有拍左片<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/150249_5d58b29a058a8dc9a4d4de52db48457b.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F150249_5d58b29a058a8dc9a4d4de52db48457b.jpeg&h=cb830943&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可惜尾段隻黑鬼又獨食又TO，轉勝為敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/150256_73c0bc13b56d8fc53ba924379b83f6bf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F150256_73c0bc13b56d8fc53ba924379b83f6bf.jpeg&h=996ba0c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2ee8d93fe0b04bd2555704486dfe8b20c521b8a","tid":828651,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:51:14.000Z","msg":"星期六4強賽程<br />\n17:00 琉球黃金帝王 vs 名古屋鑽石海豚<br />\n19:00 首爾閃電 vs 廣州龍獅"},{"pid":"f3b5bd51d16b7a860e765082aaced3ee6073a27b","tid":828651,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56f37c8b96c94275084f5ab08bea1c4b1463a0b9","tid":828651,"uid":52,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fef67397f27762de923c42547f9b144ae290b212","tid":828651,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6027a6b0cd545e9097fe53549bfa942ab4432857","tid":828651,"uid":52,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T10:31:31.000Z","msg":"我知<br />\n所以好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係呀<br />\n去過千葉主場對櫪木皇者，田臥勇太<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T12:02:37.000Z","msg":"有無相睇睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n波飛太概幾錢<br />\n日本NBA第一人仲打緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T07:17:14.000Z","msg":"買飛我係直接上佢官網買，登記做會員時需要日本地址郵區等等自己上網求奇搵個黎用就得<br />\n最貴可以握到手(?)既去到萬5円<br />\n<img src=\"https://chibajets.jp/files/rcms_conv_webp/d/0/d00e4c31609807b8fd26f04161d39958_1531122428.webp?v=1536144595\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchibajets.jp%2Ffiles%2Frcms_conv_webp%2Fd%2F0%2Fd00e4c31609807b8fd26f04161d39958_1531122428.webp%3Fv%3D1536144595&h=68ea7408&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最高山頂位就千8円<b